00:45.910 --> 00:53.570
Part 12
Even Nameless Flowers Bloom with All Their Might

01:06.530 --> 01:08.860
I was kidnapped mid-day by someone.

01:09.640 --> 01:11.860
I think my schedule will get messed up.

01:12.080 --> 01:14.000
So I'm taking measures in advance.

01:14.940 --> 01:16.810
The weather is so nice, huh?

01:17.180 --> 01:19.590
I don't know why, but I'm excited.

01:19.880 --> 01:20.920
What's wrong with you?

01:21.990 --> 01:22.960
If you change your personality,

01:22.960 --> 01:24.070
I won't re-sign with you.

01:24.070 --> 01:26.140
I can go where you go.

01:27.030 --> 01:28.220
You want me to marry you?

01:28.220 --> 01:29.220
Hey.

01:29.420 --> 01:31.520
This is a comedy, not a documentary.

01:31.520 --> 01:33.240
You won't make it on comedy shows at this rate.

01:33.240 --> 01:36.180
A comedy show that's not fun or moving

01:36.310 --> 01:37.990
should get canceled.

01:46.259 --> 01:48.890
Bbiyong is shameless and brazen.

01:48.990 --> 01:50.820
- He should be mindful...
- What?

01:50.820 --> 01:52.690
How dare he go around drunk?

01:52.710 --> 01:55.610
Does Bbiyong even know how to feel guilty?

01:55.690 --> 01:58.820
Doesn't it seem like Bbiyong is acting

01:58.820 --> 02:01.720
as if he's a solitary and free soul?

02:01.840 --> 02:03.030
What a drama queen!

02:03.030 --> 02:05.550
Why do you look so dark?

02:06.700 --> 02:07.700
It's Bbiyong.

02:08.600 --> 02:09.910
Have you heard from him?

02:10.500 --> 02:11.430
The legal team said

02:11.430 --> 02:13.990
they sent a notice about suing him for indemnity.

02:13.990 --> 02:16.070
But he said he won't stand by either,

02:16.220 --> 02:18.090
and he'll sue us for slander.

02:18.090 --> 02:19.090
Idiot.

02:20.680 --> 02:22.360
He knows he can't win so why?

02:22.360 --> 02:23.800
He's not an idiot.

02:24.240 --> 02:26.110
He just doesn't know me yet.

02:27.960 --> 02:28.900
Starpeace Director Yoon

02:29.150 --> 02:29.810
Hello?

02:29.810 --> 02:31.329
Sir, where are you?

02:31.700 --> 02:33.280
You need to come in.

02:34.250 --> 02:36.300
Let go! I said let go!

02:36.300 --> 02:38.579
- Don't film this!
- Hey! I'm Bbiyong!

02:38.610 --> 02:40.200
You know how much I did for Starpeace?

02:40.200 --> 02:41.050
- Come on.
- Hey!

02:41.050 --> 02:42.140
Bring CEO Cha.

02:42.320 --> 02:43.320
- Bring him here!
- Hey, hey, hey.

02:43.320 --> 02:44.630
- Are you ignoring me?
- Hey, hey, hey.

02:44.630 --> 02:46.060
- Go on out. Go.
- Hey!

02:46.060 --> 02:47.740
Bring CEO Cha, darn it!

02:47.920 --> 02:49.160
- Hey!
- Bring CEO Cha!

02:49.160 --> 02:50.460
- Stop this!
- Bring Che Jae-hyuk!

02:57.579 --> 02:58.579
You bastard.

02:58.600 --> 03:01.760
Hey, hey, hey, hey!

03:01.840 --> 03:03.770
- Stop this!
- Get over here!

03:03.890 --> 03:05.000
Get over here, you bastard!

03:05.000 --> 03:05.720
That's enough!

03:05.720 --> 03:06.720
Let go!

03:14.080 --> 03:15.280
You bastards...

03:16.490 --> 03:17.180
Hey!

03:17.180 --> 03:18.190
Take Ji-han away.

03:18.190 --> 03:19.190
Let go.

03:20.130 --> 03:21.550
Let go of me!

03:21.640 --> 03:22.640
Let go!

03:24.530 --> 03:27.100
Hey! You coward!

03:27.310 --> 03:29.390
Don't hide behind others like a kid.

03:29.390 --> 03:30.690
Come here, you bastard!

03:30.690 --> 03:31.690
Come here!

03:35.340 --> 03:37.020
Shut up, Bong Chung-bong.

03:37.870 --> 03:39.310
Know when to stop.

03:39.360 --> 03:40.360
Got that?

03:51.870 --> 03:53.670
I heard he drinks all day.

04:01.300 --> 04:02.980
It's not because of you.

04:03.910 --> 04:05.100
You know that, right?

04:08.550 --> 04:10.000
Darn it!

04:11.130 --> 04:12.130
It's okay.

04:14.100 --> 04:15.870
If you have something to say,

04:15.870 --> 04:17.800
come back when you're sober.

04:18.610 --> 04:19.790
There are still many

04:19.790 --> 04:22.880
who remember you as Executive Bong.

04:42.990 --> 04:43.990
Yikes!

04:46.490 --> 04:47.270
How did you get in?

04:47.270 --> 04:48.950
What's up with Bbiyong?

04:50.710 --> 04:51.750
You saw that?

04:52.750 --> 04:53.790
It's nothing.

04:54.100 --> 04:55.050
You know this.

04:55.050 --> 04:57.250
He called me several times, saying it's unfair.

04:57.250 --> 04:59.670
He received the song, but he didn't listen to it.

05:03.500 --> 05:05.120
Do you think

05:05.980 --> 05:07.340
that makes sense?

05:09.840 --> 05:10.960
Director Yoon.

05:33.000 --> 05:34.550
It was just a one-time incident.

05:34.550 --> 05:37.150
You're saying it's not news-worthy.

05:37.810 --> 05:39.370
But that's for me to decide.

05:39.390 --> 05:41.450
I'm trying to help you make a quick decision.

05:41.450 --> 05:42.540
I'll use this photo and write

05:42.540 --> 05:44.340
a romance scandal about you two.

05:44.340 --> 05:46.140
You'll have to write fiction then.

05:46.140 --> 05:47.450
I doubt that.

05:47.510 --> 05:49.159
When people see this,

05:49.159 --> 05:51.030
they won't think it's fiction.

05:53.540 --> 05:55.490
Then go ahead and write it like that.

05:56.040 --> 05:57.670
If you want to do that so much,

05:57.700 --> 05:58.990
go ahead and do it.

06:11.790 --> 06:13.570
Then go ahead and write it like that.

06:13.570 --> 06:14.940
If you want to do that so much,

06:14.960 --> 06:16.020
go ahead and do it.

06:21.500 --> 06:23.590
He won't write it as it is.

06:27.130 --> 06:29.380
Reporter Mo's interest is in Ji-han.

06:29.380 --> 06:30.160
Me?

06:30.160 --> 06:32.880
Don't you remember how he got there that day?

06:32.880 --> 06:34.320
He's not an idiot.

06:34.600 --> 06:36.810
If he writes a scandal, it'll be with Ji-han.

06:37.460 --> 06:38.180
What should I...

06:38.180 --> 06:39.850
To get what you wanted,

06:39.850 --> 06:42.050
it's true you used Ji-han.

06:42.230 --> 06:44.310
Rather than let that go public,

06:45.110 --> 06:46.860
a romance scandal about us

06:47.200 --> 06:49.030
will be less threatening to Cotton Candy.

06:49.060 --> 06:50.070
Jae-hyuk!

06:50.430 --> 06:51.210
Sir!

06:51.210 --> 06:53.010
Of course, if that happens,

06:53.350 --> 06:55.760
Cotton Candy's achievement will be belittled.

06:56.110 --> 06:57.760
They'll say you made it

06:57.790 --> 06:59.360
because I supported you.

07:00.830 --> 07:02.520
It's not like there isn't another way.

07:02.520 --> 07:04.500
It's not like we didn't expect this.

07:05.070 --> 07:06.320
If things go bad,

07:06.340 --> 07:08.340
I'll use the information I gathered.

07:10.020 --> 07:13.150
Let's see what Reporter Mo does for now.

07:13.560 --> 07:14.560
Grandma.

07:14.730 --> 07:17.050
Why do you sound so weak?

07:17.050 --> 07:18.090
Are you sick?

07:18.250 --> 07:19.840
Not at all.

07:20.470 --> 07:22.470
I ate so much

07:22.780 --> 07:27.050
that I was dozing off like a chick in a nest.

07:27.050 --> 07:29.590
Don't just eat vegetables. Eat meat.

07:29.590 --> 07:31.410
I sent you a hefty allowance.

07:31.410 --> 07:32.350
Spend it!

07:32.350 --> 07:33.830
Okay.

07:34.659 --> 07:37.000
Okay, let's hang up now.

07:37.000 --> 07:38.620
What about the tonic I sent you?

07:38.620 --> 07:39.820
Are you taking that well?

07:39.820 --> 07:41.630
My fan sent it to me.

07:42.060 --> 07:43.550
It's really expensive.

07:43.550 --> 07:45.440
Don't forget to take it every day.

07:45.440 --> 07:47.120
Okay, I won't forget.

07:48.140 --> 07:50.100
I'm hanging up now.

07:51.180 --> 07:52.360
Grandma.

07:52.460 --> 07:53.770
I miss you.

07:53.890 --> 07:55.720
Can't you come to Seoul for a visit?

07:55.720 --> 07:57.860
If you get to Seoul Station, I'll go pick you up.

07:57.860 --> 07:59.580
I don't have time to go down.

07:59.580 --> 08:01.020
I don't, either.

08:01.770 --> 08:03.160
Let's hang up now.

08:03.160 --> 08:05.430
Why do you keep trying to hang up?

08:05.910 --> 08:07.360
What about the village head?

08:07.360 --> 08:09.040
Does he come by often?

08:09.090 --> 08:10.890
Does your new TV work well?

08:17.810 --> 08:20.050
Dan's song is getting a great response.

08:20.050 --> 08:22.220
Many are saying Chae-ah's voice is addictive.

08:22.380 --> 08:23.980
You mooched off Dan.

08:24.460 --> 08:25.800
Jeez.

08:25.960 --> 08:27.880
Just pretend to not notice.

08:32.640 --> 08:34.250
You know what Hyun-ji said?

08:34.409 --> 08:36.110
That I was the missing member

08:36.140 --> 08:37.070
in her dream.

08:37.100 --> 08:38.270
Haa!

08:38.340 --> 08:39.900
That I'll be hospitalized because

08:39.919 --> 08:41.250
Calla will attack me.

08:42.799 --> 08:44.270
Okay!

08:44.270 --> 08:45.780
I'll send Seok-chun out

08:45.780 --> 08:47.560
to the station at your arrival time.

08:47.690 --> 08:48.690
Okay.

08:48.970 --> 08:50.770
Wear the red scarf I bought you

08:50.770 --> 08:52.030
- and stand still.
- It's really good.

08:52.030 --> 08:53.380
Don't go anywhere.

08:53.380 --> 08:55.580
Even if you have to pee. Okay?

08:56.320 --> 08:57.540
Okay.

08:57.770 --> 08:59.880
Alright. I'll hang up now.

08:59.930 --> 09:01.050
Bye!

09:01.890 --> 09:02.920
Your grandma's coming?

09:02.920 --> 09:04.150
Yeah.

09:04.150 --> 09:05.780
She refused at first.

09:05.780 --> 09:07.860
But she misses her pretty granddaughter.

09:09.290 --> 09:10.610
When she gets here,

09:10.610 --> 09:11.850
she said she'll cook for us.

09:12.370 --> 09:13.140
Really?

09:13.140 --> 09:14.920
Yeah! I'm so happy!

09:15.010 --> 09:16.960
- I'm glad.
- I look forward to it.

09:18.750 --> 09:20.830
I'm Bbiyong!

09:21.330 --> 09:22.630
I'm here.

09:23.010 --> 09:26.170
Bring CEO Cha! Bring him to me!

09:26.530 --> 09:27.290
You bastard.

09:27.290 --> 09:29.090
What are you watching?

09:29.750 --> 09:31.620
I said bring CEO Cha!

09:31.620 --> 09:33.620
You saw him for the first time yesterday, huh?

09:36.090 --> 09:37.090
Yeah.

09:37.120 --> 09:39.590
I heard he lives like a total zombie.

09:41.310 --> 09:43.050
He called the other guys a few times.

09:43.300 --> 09:44.470
He was drunk.

09:45.110 --> 09:46.390
What did he say?

09:46.590 --> 09:48.110
That it was unfair.

09:48.280 --> 09:49.550
He was griping.

09:49.550 --> 09:51.890
Kept talking about the good old days.

09:53.460 --> 09:55.140
It's not pleasant to see

09:55.150 --> 09:56.450
a hero fall.

10:04.980 --> 10:06.020
Wow.

10:06.040 --> 10:07.110
Bbyong, that bastard.

10:07.110 --> 10:08.550
He's unbelievable.

10:08.640 --> 10:10.980
He still hasn't come to his senses.

10:11.510 --> 10:14.350
You know he kicked up a fuss here yesterday?

10:14.880 --> 10:15.830
What is it?

10:17.310 --> 10:18.500
No way.

10:19.410 --> 10:22.380
I heard he goes around saying he'll ruin us.

10:23.510 --> 10:25.300
He's such a phony big talker.

10:25.300 --> 10:27.750
How in the world will he ruin us?

10:27.750 --> 10:30.210
If he keeps causing a fuss like this,

10:30.250 --> 10:32.850
bad public opinion can form against us.

10:33.840 --> 10:35.960
Regardless of who was right or wrong.

10:38.410 --> 10:39.410
Bbiyong.

10:39.820 --> 10:41.070
Hang in there.

10:41.070 --> 10:43.060
We only have a few more days left.

10:54.660 --> 10:56.620
Hey, isn't that Bbiyong?

10:56.620 --> 10:57.510
Bbiyong?

10:57.510 --> 10:59.360
I heard he plagiarized.

10:59.500 --> 11:01.180
I should take a picture.

11:01.510 --> 11:03.200
- Let's take a photo.
- What's he doing?

11:03.250 --> 11:04.690
We'll upload this.

11:10.520 --> 11:12.240
He knows they're taking his photo.

11:15.260 --> 11:16.570
He's letting them.

11:16.570 --> 11:17.570
Why?

11:18.330 --> 11:21.130
To create noise. To make it into an issue.

11:21.130 --> 11:22.930
Cotton Candy is the target.

11:23.160 --> 11:23.950
To taint their image.

11:23.950 --> 11:25.830
That's stupid.

11:26.450 --> 11:28.680
He's ruining himself, too.

11:29.410 --> 11:31.820
Does he only think of getting revenge?

11:31.820 --> 11:33.060
Even after...

11:33.750 --> 11:35.510
Even after what he did?

11:49.490 --> 11:50.490
Stop.

11:52.840 --> 11:54.760
I heard you're CEO Ma's favorite.

11:54.760 --> 11:55.250
What?

11:55.250 --> 11:56.530
Do you know who I am?

11:56.530 --> 11:59.600
Yes. Starpeace's leading producer, Bbiyong.

11:59.600 --> 12:00.600
Come on.

12:00.900 --> 12:02.390
You left something out.

12:02.390 --> 12:03.390
Oh.

12:03.930 --> 12:05.790
Genius leading producer, Bbiyong.

12:08.950 --> 12:09.980
Sit down.

12:10.580 --> 12:11.860
I said sit down.

12:13.980 --> 12:14.980
Stand up.

12:17.420 --> 12:18.420
Sit down.

12:19.560 --> 12:20.680
Stand up.

12:22.850 --> 12:24.720
Don't stand up but sit down.

12:24.850 --> 12:27.370
Don't sit down. Don't stand up.

12:27.610 --> 12:28.810
Sit down.

12:29.540 --> 12:30.540
Hey.

12:32.090 --> 12:33.920
You always do as you're told?

12:33.920 --> 12:34.920
What?

12:38.280 --> 12:40.270
You're not CEO Ma's favorite.

12:41.000 --> 12:42.520
You're my favorite.

12:43.160 --> 12:44.730
You cute rascal.

12:45.940 --> 12:46.940
Hey.

12:47.240 --> 12:49.430
You're a promising rough stone.

12:49.880 --> 12:52.470
I'll sharpen and polish you

12:52.710 --> 12:54.570
so you'll become a gemstone.

13:00.300 --> 13:02.920
Our agency might look shabby now.

13:03.440 --> 13:04.880
But I'm confident.

13:05.930 --> 13:06.930
Look.

13:07.130 --> 13:08.490
I'm going to make

13:08.620 --> 13:10.620
everything here kneel at my feet.

13:12.140 --> 13:14.620
Want me to make them kneel at your feet, too?

13:17.660 --> 13:18.740
Hey!

13:19.260 --> 13:21.020
Wait!

13:21.190 --> 13:23.530
Here we come!

13:33.590 --> 13:35.710
Hey, Ji-han! Ji-han! Hey!

13:35.900 --> 13:36.900
Hey!

13:37.040 --> 13:38.440
Plagiarizing Bbyong.

13:38.620 --> 13:40.460
Don't live like that.

13:40.850 --> 13:44.580
How can you steal from my Cotton Candy?

13:44.750 --> 13:46.850
What's there to steal from them?

13:46.850 --> 13:48.260
Why'd you do it? Speak.

13:48.440 --> 13:49.560
That's him?

13:49.560 --> 13:51.140
The guy who stole from Cotton Candy?

13:51.140 --> 13:52.330
Yeah.

13:52.530 --> 13:55.190
He looks like he'll plagiarize.

13:55.190 --> 13:57.080
Yeah, he looks so sneaky.

13:57.080 --> 13:59.010
Plagiarizing Bbyong, Bbyong, Bbyong.

13:59.010 --> 14:00.740
Shut up, you bastards.

14:02.120 --> 14:03.210
You crazy?

14:03.210 --> 14:04.210
What?

14:13.400 --> 14:16.190
I should just crush you.

14:16.830 --> 14:18.920
- Ji-han, Ji-han.
- It's Mars.

14:19.430 --> 14:21.370
- It's Ji-han.
- Don't take photos.

14:22.070 --> 14:23.510
Don't take photos!

14:24.390 --> 14:25.390
Go now.

14:25.410 --> 14:26.410
Go!

14:26.480 --> 14:27.480
Film him.

14:28.280 --> 14:29.140
Bbiyong!

14:29.140 --> 14:30.750
- Bbiyong!
- It's Mars.

14:30.750 --> 14:32.660
We have to get this.

14:32.660 --> 14:33.550
Don't take photos.

14:33.550 --> 14:34.990
Don't take photos!

14:35.010 --> 14:36.700
Jeez!

14:36.730 --> 14:38.770
- Go now.
- Jeez.

14:38.790 --> 14:39.610
Jeez.

14:39.610 --> 14:41.180
That idiot.

14:42.430 --> 14:45.080
Why is Ji-han there?

14:46.530 --> 14:48.430
It'll be hard for him.

14:49.100 --> 14:52.170
The rumor Bbiyong raised Ji-han to his status...

14:53.610 --> 14:55.740
Half is wrong and half is right.

14:56.990 --> 14:58.830
I'm upset with Bbiyong.

14:59.770 --> 15:01.770
But seeing him like that makes me feel bad.

15:01.900 --> 15:03.850
He got his comeuppance.

15:03.850 --> 15:05.070
I'm happy.

15:06.400 --> 15:08.080
You don't look happy.

15:08.670 --> 15:09.830
What?

15:10.120 --> 15:12.140
I'm happy. I'm so happy.

15:13.020 --> 15:14.970
Whatever. Let's practice.

15:14.970 --> 15:16.900
We don't have time to dawdle.

15:17.100 --> 15:18.630
There's only a few days left. Come on.

15:19.410 --> 15:21.570
Don't drag your feet!

15:21.570 --> 15:22.570
Okay, okay.

15:22.940 --> 15:23.720
Let's go.

15:24.190 --> 15:25.870
Let's practice, Jenna.

16:02.170 --> 16:03.290
Why am I here?

16:06.810 --> 16:08.600
Are you going to keep living like this?

16:11.490 --> 16:12.770
Why ask me that?

16:14.850 --> 16:16.710
The ones who made me like this

16:17.700 --> 16:18.740
are you guys.

16:18.740 --> 16:19.740
No.

16:21.040 --> 16:23.040
The one who made you like that

16:23.360 --> 16:24.360
is you.

16:24.630 --> 16:25.580
What?

16:25.580 --> 16:27.330
Everyone in Korea knows.

16:27.890 --> 16:29.890
Why don't you?

16:30.380 --> 16:31.980
You know, don't you?

16:33.200 --> 16:34.820
The ones who made me like this

16:34.820 --> 16:37.130
are Kim Jenna, Seo Ji-han, Cha Jae-hyuk,

16:37.130 --> 16:39.090
Cotton Candy, Starpeace...

16:40.100 --> 16:41.450
All those crappy bastards.

16:41.450 --> 16:42.450
No.

16:42.610 --> 16:43.610
You know.

16:43.960 --> 16:45.970
That's why you're acting out!

16:45.970 --> 16:46.970
What?

16:50.170 --> 16:51.170
You should

16:51.930 --> 16:53.510
apologize to yourself.

16:53.510 --> 16:55.460
You were brilliant and talented.

16:55.460 --> 16:57.180
At one time, you were someone's role model.

16:57.180 --> 16:58.910
Apologize to that Bbiyong!

17:01.040 --> 17:03.270
Tell him you're sorry you ruined him.

17:09.750 --> 17:12.420
I don't want to hear your cheap lecture.

17:12.550 --> 17:13.550
Bbiyong!

17:17.710 --> 17:19.450
Your old songs

17:19.760 --> 17:21.119
were really good.

17:21.960 --> 17:23.470
They were so good

17:23.589 --> 17:26.190
that they didn't need more description.

17:28.660 --> 17:31.730
Many kids dreamt of song-writing because of you.

17:34.820 --> 17:36.020
You should have

17:37.320 --> 17:39.340
trusted yourself more.

17:42.530 --> 17:44.120
It's not too late.

17:46.020 --> 17:47.700
Go back to that Bbiyong.

17:53.940 --> 17:54.940
I can't.

17:57.700 --> 17:58.700
Now,

18:00.110 --> 18:01.530
I can't go back.

