26:21.800 --> 26:23.430
You became best friends.

26:23.430 --> 26:26.790
You were trainees at different agencies

26:26.930 --> 26:28.830
but Hyun-ji debuted

26:30.620 --> 26:33.000
and you didn't.

26:33.720 --> 26:34.720
Reporter Mo.

26:36.400 --> 26:37.890
You got it wrong.

26:38.130 --> 26:38.730
What?

26:38.730 --> 26:40.640
Hyun-ji became a trainee.

26:41.190 --> 26:43.190
I didn't even become that.

26:43.440 --> 26:45.650
