27:11.320 --> 27:12.190
Ae-rin...

27:12.190 --> 27:13.200
Jenna.

27:14.840 --> 27:17.280
I sometimes do jobs as an extra.

27:17.740 --> 27:18.820
Did you know?

27:20.020 --> 27:21.700
That even among extras,

27:21.800 --> 27:24.710
there's a lead, supporting role, and minor role.

27:24.710 --> 27:27.450
If you're shown next to the star, it's the lead.

27:27.450 --> 27:29.980
If you just pass by, you're a supporting role.

27:30.170 --> 27:31.290
If you filmed,

27:32.050 --> 27:33.620
