27:33.820 --> 27:35.020
you're a minor role.

27:37.280 --> 27:38.110
I thought

27:38.110 --> 27:40.540
Hyun-ji and I were extras in this business.

27:41.590 --> 27:43.270
But Hyun-ji was the lead

27:43.450 --> 27:44.730
and I was always

27:46.470 --> 27:48.960
the supporting or minor role.

27:50.480 --> 27:51.330
Ae-rin...

27:51.330 --> 27:52.330
Jenna.

27:53.610 --> 27:56.340
The reason I thought Hyun-ji was the lead

27:57.530 --> 27:59.550
wasn't because she debuted.

28:03.340 --> 28:04.460
It was because

28:05.980 --> 28:07.660
Hyun-ji had partners.

28:09.880 --> 28:11.390
I envied her for that.

28:12.930 --> 28:14.610
When I was with Hyun-ji,

28:15.310 --> 28:17.630
I felt like I was a part of Cotton Candy.

28:18.510 --> 28:20.780
I wouldn't have made it if I was alone.

28:40.120 --> 28:41.120
Ae-rin.

28:42.810 --> 28:44.490
You're a part of us, too.

28:46.020 --> 28:47.140
You're family.

28:48.430 --> 28:49.710
We all feel

28:51.150 --> 28:52.750
