28:53.400 --> 28:55.200
When Cotton Candy disbands,

28:55.800 --> 28:57.240
I'll disband, too.

29:00.370 --> 29:01.370
Jenna.

29:02.420 --> 29:03.700
Please make No.1

29:04.130 --> 29:05.130
