40:44.010 --> 40:51.170
Over Arirang hill you go

40:53.070 --> 40:57.540
My love, you are...

40:59.130 --> 41:00.170
Leaving me...

41:07.950 --> 41:09.120
Grandma.

41:11.190 --> 41:12.280
Grandma.

41:13.420 --> 41:14.710
Can you hear me?

41:17.800 --> 41:20.890
You always asked me to sing "Arirang."

41:23.630 --> 41:26.980
