42:19.930 --> 42:20.930
I see.

42:21.760 --> 42:22.840
Jenna.

42:23.930 --> 42:25.110
Hyun-ji's grandmother...

42:25.890 --> 42:27.820
I promise you she'll wake up.

42:29.400 --> 42:32.300
