42:40.550 --> 42:41.550
Hold on.

42:43.500 --> 42:46.810
Kim Jenna

42:50.670 --> 42:51.670
Jenna.

42:52.630 --> 42:53.990
It's me, Hyun-ji.

42:57.490 --> 42:58.660
Hyun-ji...

43:03.690 --> 43:05.220
