43:54.560 --> 43:55.880
I know...

43:57.080 --> 43:58.290
I know...

44:01.000 --> 44:03.760
I know all this.

44:06.380 --> 44:08.020
But I can't go.

44:08.530 --> 44:11.650
I can't leave my grandma.

44:17.700 --> 44:19.380
I won't say I'm sorry.

44:52.970 --> 44:54.150
The four of us

44:55.550 --> 44:57.230
