46:52.830 --> 46:53.830
Oh Hyun-ji!

46:54.570 --> 46:55.570
Oh Hyun-ji!

47:01.670 --> 47:02.670
Grandma!

47:03.140 --> 47:04.140
Grandma!

47:04.210 --> 47:06.300
Are you awake? Huh?

47:06.620 --> 47:09.110
Open your eyes! Huh?

47:09.200 --> 47:10.400
Open your eyes!

47:10.560 --> 47:12.070
It's me, Hyun-ji.

47:12.070 --> 47:14.290
Are you awake? Huh?

47:14.290 --> 47:15.640
- Grandma!
- Hyun-ji, move over for a second.

47:15.640 --> 47:16.640
- Are you awake?
- Come on!

47:16.640 --> 47:18.390
