- Grandma! Grandma!

47:18.730 --> 47:21.130
Grandma, are you awake? Grandma!

47:21.130 --> 47:29.640
- Hello, we're Unlady.
- Hello, we're Unlady.

47:40.580 --> 47:41.580
You did well.

47:42.730 --> 47:43.730
Good job.

47:44.310 --> 47:46.050
I'll tell the director Cotton Candy

47:46.050 --> 47:48.440
