48:13.330 --> 48:14.330
She woke up?

48:17.100 --> 48:18.020
No.

48:18.020 --> 48:21.290
You're awake, right?

48:21.630 --> 48:25.670
Open your eyes! Come on and open them!

48:26.570 --> 48:27.690
Go...

48:28.040 --> 48:29.600
Huh?

48:30.400 --> 48:32.390
Huh? What?

48:33.240 --> 48:35.170
Go...

48:36.090 --> 48:37.860
Grandma... Grandma!

48:37.880 --> 48:40.010
Grandma, it's me Hyun-ji.

48:40.010 --> 48:41.620
Grandma! Grandma!

48:41.620 --> 48:43.330
Grandma, I love you.

48:43.330 --> 48:44.950
Grandma! Grandma!

48:44.950 --> 48:47.870
- Please step away.
- It's me, Hyun-ji.

48:47.920 --> 48:49.130
- Come on.
- Grandma!

48:49.130 --> 48:52.390
My grandma spoke.

48:52.390 --> 48:52.990
- Ma'am?
- Calm down.

48:52.990 --> 48:54.550
- Grandma!
- Calm down, Hyun-ji.

48:54.550 --> 48:56.650
