48:56.650 --> 48:57.960
My grandma spoke.

48:57.960 --> 49:00.400
My grandma spoke, okay?

49:00.400 --> 49:01.520
Grandma!

49:02.460 --> 49:04.940
It's me, Hyun-ji. Grandma!

49:05.210 --> 49:06.280
Grandma...

49:06.330 --> 49:07.700
She hasn't gained consciousness yet.

49:07.760 --> 49:09.650
Please step out for a while to calm down.

49:09.650 --> 49:10.530
You're wrong!

49:10.530 --> 49:12.550
My grandma spoke!

49:12.570 --> 49:14.940
- Let's go.
- My grandma spoke!

49:14.950 --> 49:17.320
- My grandma spoke!
- Okay, okay.

49:17.320 --> 49:18.390
Grandma...

49:18.390 --> 49:20.260
She can't wake up.

49:21.160 --> 49:23.040
But she told me to go.

49:24.410 --> 49:25.850
She told me to go.

49:26.920 --> 49:27.920
Okay.

49:28.860 --> 49:29.860
Hurry here.

49:30.930 --> 49:31.930
Okay.

49:41.590 --> 49:42.630
She's coming.

49:50.910 --> 49:52.270
You'll be able to

49:52.450 --> 49:54.320
