49:55.000 --> 49:57.560
Mr. Gyeong-tak, if something happens...

49:57.560 --> 49:58.560
Okay.

49:58.620 --> 49:59.930
If something happens,

49:59.930 --> 50:01.610
I'll call you right away.

50:01.720 --> 50:02.920
So don't worry.

50:05.020 --> 50:06.020
Okay.

51:00.010 --> 51:01.930
- Hyun-ji!
- Hyun-ji!

51:28.800 --> 51:30.620
Mr. Gyeong-tak

51:48.290 --> 51:49.290
Here.

51:57.600 --> 51:58.960
Mr. Gyeong-tak...

52:01.390 --> 52:02.770
Mr. Gyeong-tak!

52:02.940 --> 52:05.500
Why aren't you saying anything?

52:08.400 --> 52:09.980
Hyun-ji...

52:11.830 --> 52:12.830
Grandma?

52:15.180 --> 52:16.180
Grandma!

52:16.860 --> 52:18.110
Are you awake?

52:18.670 --> 52:20.220
Have you come to?

52:20.730 --> 52:22.400
It's me, Hyun-ji!

52:22.640 --> 52:23.640
Yeah.

52:24.600 --> 52:27.840
Will you be on TV?

52:28.620 --> 52:29.620
Wow.

52:30.680 --> 52:32.730
I'm proud of you, my baby.

52:38.490 --> 52:39.490
Hello?

52:40.070 --> 52:41.390
Hyun-ji!

52:41.670 --> 52:43.260
Your grandma is awake.

52:43.940 --> 52:46.480
She says not to worry and do what you do.

52:48.100 --> 52:49.300
Okay.

52:51.640 --> 52:52.640
Let's go.

52:53.910 --> 52:54.910
Jenna!

53:11.800 --> 53:14.300
Such explosive energy, firing up the fans!

53:14.300 --> 53:16.450
We just saw Unlady's performance.

53:16.450 --> 53:19.540
The poll for real-time voting will close soon.

53:19.540 --> 53:20.650
So please hurry.

53:20.650 --> 53:23.920
Now, we'll see the teams that'll be the finale.

53:23.920 --> 53:25.190
It's the No.1 candidates.

53:25.190 --> 53:27.920
First, it's KillA who's been No.1 for 3 weeks.

53:28.070 --> 53:30.690
Will they be able to keep their No.1 position?

53:30.690 --> 53:33.830
This is KillA's "Shalala," the next K-pop queens.

53:41.970 --> 53:44.280
At this perfect moment

53:44.280 --> 53:46.350
I encounter the real me

53:46.350 --> 53:48.210
Me, me (Me, me, me)

53:48.210 --> 53:50.270
Oh, me, me (Me, me, me)

53:50.270 --> 53:52.540
Don't be stuck in an obvious frame

53:52.630 --> 53:55.480
The star of this stage is me

53:55.480 --> 53:56.580
Me, me (Me, me, me)

53:56.580 --> 53:58.420
Oh, me, me (Me, me, me)

53:58.420 --> 54:00.750
I wanna dance the night away

54:00.750 --> 54:02.910
Just dance the night away

54:02.910 --> 54:05.130
The spotlight shines on me

54:05.130 --> 54:07.270
Ride the rhythm like bam bam bam

54:07.270 --> 54:11.370
The brighter the light, the more dazzling it is

54:11.370 --> 54:13.500
Wherever I go, I shine brightly

54:13.500 --> 54:15.090
Fly away Tinkerbell

54:15.090 --> 54:18.430
I'm fully prepared

54:19.240 --> 54:22.480
You know you can't reject me

54:22.660 --> 54:23.970
Baby love me now

54:23.970 --> 54:25.990
From my head to my toes

54:25.990 --> 54:27.870
I'm nothing like your expectations

54:27.870 --> 54:30.420
I can't be explained

54:30.460 --> 54:32.460
Everything about me is Shalala

54:36.490 --> 54:38.860
When the stars shine in the night sky

54:38.860 --> 54:40.500
Everything about me is Shalala

54:40.500 --> 54:42.720
Wow! KillA's performance is overwhelming.

54:42.720 --> 54:44.970
Cotton Candy is up next.

54:44.970 --> 54:46.480
KillA VS Cotton Candy.

54:46.620 --> 54:49.160
The real-time comment section is on fire.

54:49.160 --> 54:50.400
I'll ask my subscribers.

54:50.420 --> 54:52.080
Who do you think will win?

54:52.100 --> 54:53.360
This is so exciting!

54:53.630 --> 54:54.530
Hey, ya'll.

54:54.530 --> 54:56.470
Don't you think Cotton Candy will make No.1?

54:56.470 --> 54:58.090
The don't have an album score,

54:58.090 --> 55:00.800
but they have the united fandom.

55:02.770 --> 55:04.760
There will be voting via text...

55:04.760 --> 55:06.740
So there's the official fans, Candies.

55:06.740 --> 55:08.360
There's also Calla fans.

55:08.360 --> 55:11.170
And there are small and medium sized fanclubs.

55:11.380 --> 55:13.520
Tearful fanclubs because their stars disbanded.

55:13.520 --> 55:15.510
And fanclubs of ancestor idols in the 2000s.

55:15.510 --> 55:17.320
The united fanclubs have all gathered.

55:17.320 --> 55:18.350
What does this mean?

55:18.350 --> 55:20.000
That Cotton Candy's story

55:20.000 --> 55:22.210
sounds like my story!

55:22.980 --> 55:24.020
Cotton Candy!

55:24.190 --> 55:25.570
Let's be happy!

55:25.690 --> 55:26.890
Let's be happy!

55:27.180 --> 55:31.710
Cotton Candy! Cotton Candy!

55:32.050 --> 55:33.420
For the past 3 months...

55:34.090 --> 55:35.380
No regrets, right?

55:35.410 --> 55:36.770
- Right!
- Right!

55:37.810 --> 55:39.530
You did all you wanted to do, right?

55:39.530 --> 55:40.850
- Right!
- Right!

55:41.610 --> 55:44.060
Let's make it so that when we think of today

55:44.600 --> 55:46.340
in the future, we'll have no regrets.

55:46.340 --> 55:47.790
Okay.

55:48.340 --> 55:49.170
Okay.

55:49.220 --> 55:50.740
Let's pour out everything!

55:50.740 --> 55:52.270
- Everything!
- Everything!

55:54.440 --> 55:55.290
Ta-da!

55:55.300 --> 55:56.420
CEO Ma's ring.

55:56.960 --> 55:58.120
Me, too.

55:58.860 --> 56:00.060
CEO Ma...

56:07.490 --> 56:08.490
Cot!

56:10.380 --> 56:11.380
Ton!

56:12.280 --> 56:13.280
Can!

56:14.220 --> 56:15.220
Dy!

56:20.040 --> 56:21.160
Let's disband!

56:54.460 --> 56:56.210
Another candidate for No.1!

56:56.210 --> 56:57.750
They made No.1 on the single's chart and

56:57.750 --> 57:00.370
became a No.1 candidate in the music show.

57:00.480 --> 57:02.000
It's not just Korea.

57:02.000 --> 57:04.700
The whole universe roots for them.

57:04.700 --> 57:06.830
This is Cotton Candy's "Finale."

57:24.680 --> 57:26.640
Try me, What's wrong with me?

57:26.910 --> 57:29.120
You hate me, I'll show you who I am

57:29.200 --> 57:31.100
Baby, I gotta live it up

57:33.630 --> 57:35.700
Try me, What's wrong with me?

57:35.850 --> 57:38.020
You hate me, Now I've changed

57:38.560 --> 57:40.620
I love Cotton Candy.

57:40.970 --> 57:43.880
You'll be like cotton candy that gives

57:43.880 --> 57:47.170
comfort, happiness and love to the world.

57:48.620 --> 57:49.620
Look.

57:50.680 --> 57:52.420
I'm going to be like that.

57:52.710 --> 57:54.730
A star you can see anywhere in the world.

57:55.020 --> 57:56.320
I'm going to be like that star.

57:56.320 --> 57:57.360
No matter what.

57:59.050 --> 58:00.340
I want to get out.

58:01.220 --> 58:02.660
Whatever I become,

58:02.800 --> 58:04.930
I want to grow up outside this booth.

58:07.580 --> 58:09.180
I'm not unfortunate.

58:09.710 --> 58:10.710
I won't let

58:11.020 --> 58:12.460
my world be shaken

58:12.540 --> 58:13.980
by something else.

58:16.130 --> 58:17.130
Grandma!

58:17.680 --> 58:19.040
Are you watching?

58:19.400 --> 58:21.050
You're watching, right?

58:21.260 --> 58:22.860
I'm Oh Hyun-ji!

58:26.020 --> 58:27.320
To be a good agent

58:27.350 --> 58:29.030
for a successful Cotton Candy.

58:30.220 --> 58:31.500
That's my dream.

58:31.860 --> 58:32.860
So you all

58:33.010 --> 58:34.290
have to make it.

58:37.790 --> 58:38.790
Finally,

58:40.140 --> 58:41.140
it's over.

58:42.080 --> 58:43.080
We did well.

58:44.070 --> 58:45.090
All of us.

58:46.720 --> 58:47.960
We did so well.

58:49.860 --> 58:51.150
Good job.

58:52.660 --> 58:53.880
Cotton Candy.

59:00.920 --> 59:03.510
Can you feel this trembling?

59:03.510 --> 59:08.140
Do you feel the same way?

59:08.420 --> 59:12.950
Time has stopped as if I'm in a dream

59:14.280 --> 59:16.100
This is great!

59:17.640 --> 59:19.670
It's the ocean!

59:27.410 --> 59:29.640
