59:29.640 --> 59:31.320
That's no fun.

59:31.320 --> 59:31.750
Huh?

59:31.750 --> 59:33.710
Jae-hyuk, you talk too much.

59:35.280 --> 59:36.170
Why are you so stressed out?

59:36.170 --> 59:38.100
You guys are on a hiatus now.

59:38.610 --> 59:39.380
I'll enlist you in the army.

59:39.380 --> 59:40.580
- What?
- What?

59:57.580 --> 59:59.220
What are you going to do now?

1:00:03.680 --> 1:00:04.820
I don't know.

1:00:06.190 --> 1:00:07.590
What should I do first?

1:00:07.790 --> 1:00:10.340
I thought this was the only thing for me.

1:00:11.590 --> 1:00:13.270
But after letting it go,

1:00:13.940 --> 1:00:16.760
I see there's so much more I can do.

1:00:18.840 --> 1:00:20.610
There's so much more I want to do.

1:00:21.500 --> 1:00:23.790
You must be multi-talented.

1:00:24.160 --> 1:00:24.970
I envy you.

1:00:28.020 --> 1:00:29.510
Come on, Jenna!

1:00:29.820 --> 1:00:30.820
Okay!

1:00:34.490 --> 1:00:36.090
This place is great.

1:00:36.720 --> 1:00:38.030
You're free tomorrow, right?

1:00:38.030 --> 1:00:38.960
Let's go.

1:00:38.960 --> 1:00:39.960
Where?

1:00:40.470 --> 1:00:41.410
There?

1:00:41.410 --> 1:00:42.410
Yeah.

1:00:43.730 --> 1:00:45.910
Nobody will disrupt us now.

1:00:46.560 --> 1:00:48.720
Why do you keep asking me to go there?

1:00:48.720 --> 1:00:49.720
Remember you buried

1:00:50.930 --> 1:00:54.000
