1:01:03.020 --> 1:01:04.700
What did you put inside?

1:01:05.010 --> 1:01:06.010
Oh!

1:01:06.410 --> 1:01:08.210
Are you talking about that?

1:01:08.680 --> 1:01:09.920
What is it?

1:01:10.160 --> 1:01:11.630
Something we could open in 20 years?

1:01:11.630 --> 1:01:14.060
You talking about what Wendy asked me to do?

1:01:15.870 --> 1:01:16.540
Wendy?

1:01:16.540 --> 1:01:17.810
You don't know Wendy?

1:01:17.810 --> 1:01:19.290
She lived in our neighborhood.

1:01:19.290 --> 1:01:21.250
She was a tomboy.

1:01:21.250 --> 1:01:23.220
A redhead with a lot of freckles.

1:01:23.220 --> 1:01:25.230
She always braided her hair into pigtails.

1:01:25.230 --> 1:01:26.580
She was really strong.

1:01:26.580 --> 1:01:28.100
Oh, right.

1:01:28.360 --> 1:01:29.370
What about her?

1:01:29.370 --> 1:01:31.310
She liked you.

1:01:32.220 --> 1:01:34.900
She asked me to bury something in the yard.

1:01:34.900 --> 1:01:38.240
You know she was superstitious, right?

1:01:39.590 --> 1:01:42.000
She said she could marry you if I buried it.

1:01:42.000 --> 1:01:43.000
So?

1:01:43.460 --> 1:01:44.550
What did you bury?

1:01:44.570 --> 1:01:46.900
Her fingernail and toenail clippings.

1:01:46.900 --> 1:01:49.160
She even cut off pieces of her hair.

1:01:50.120 --> 1:01:51.120
That...

